            . I have known Harling about five years; I never; knew him have a bad character in my life; he is a <rs id="t17721209-22-deflabel129" type="occupation">lamp-lighter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17721209-22-defend262 t17721209-22-deflabel129"></join>, he worked for Mr. Pearce, in Holborn.</p>
